Program: Outlook
Title: Khmer Rouge Leaders Face Their Victims
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrfp
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
As Cambodia brings Khmer Rouge leaders to trial, survivors face their torturers at forums. Also, Dot.com companies taking over the world - can their foundations take the strain? Traditional businessman Victor Kiam comments. Finally, prostitution and a visit to the brothels of the Red Light District in Amsterdam. Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less